# MCP Server Template

This is a template for creating new MCP servers.

## Usage

1. Copy this template folder
2. Rename it to your MCP server name
3. Update `package.json` with your server details
4. Implement your tools in `src/index.ts`
5. Build and test

## Development

npm installnpm run buildnpm run dev


## Registering with Gemini CLI

Add to `.gemini/settings.json`:

{“mcp”: {“servers”: {“your-server-name”: {“command”: “node”,“args”: “mcp/your-folder/dist/index.js”,“cwd”: “.”}}}}